Package: gradR
Title: Theoretical Gradient Descent and Optimization Diagnostic
        Dashboard
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Rachit Jindal
Maintainer: Rachit Jindal <rachitj24@iitk.ac.in>
Description: An interactive, educational visualization tool for mathematical 
    optimization. This package provides a dynamic Shiny dashboard to explore 
    first-order gradient descent paths, evaluate second-order Hessian 
    conditions for saddle point diagnostics, and simulate Stochastic Gradient 
    Descent (SGD) with dynamic learning rate decay.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, plotly, shiny
NeedsCompilation: no
Packaged: 2026-04-03 17:41:05 UTC; rajan
